# Fitness AI Coach V2 - Cursor Rules

## Project Structure
- Monorepo with Turbo
- `apps/web` - Next.js 16 application
- `packages/ai` - AI/LLM package
- `packages/supabase` - Supabase client/server

## Key Technologies
- Next.js 16 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Supabase (Auth, Database, RLS)
- Ollama (Local LLM)
- Tailwind CSS

## Important Files
- `COMPLETE_IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md` - Main implementation plan
- `database_blueprint_v1.md` - Database schema

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript strictly
- Follow Next.js 16 App Router conventions
- Use Supabase for authentication and database
- Keep components simple and reusable

